ally confident.<br/><br/>At one point, my manager asked if she could go through some details herself.<br/>I happily handed over my laptop and sat back, feeling like the most organized intern in the room 🫩😭<br/><br/>Meanwhile, I opened my phone and started chatting with fellow interns.<br/><br/>You know... the usual stuff:<br/><br/><br/>What I had completely forgotten was one tiny detail.<br/><br/>My WhatsApp was logged into my laptop.<br/>And every.<br/>Single.<br/>Message.<br/><br/>Was popping up on the screen that my manager was currently using.<br/><br/>Informal groups Notifications<br/>Random Blame Game Notifications<br/><br/>Skipped a beat for a moment<br/>Thankfully she didn't read last message 💀 (otherwise 😭)<br/><br/>To every new Intern- just double check everything, don't rush 🫡<br/><br/><br/>Now I am open to just Remote Jobs😭<button class="f1fc7b4e _387b63ad _410f0022 _9c13cf28 d56d3720 _40bf2a58 fda4ef77 e881c29d _17d59b94 _9c968625 _8301dc9e _354585b3 efbda1ba _97eda185 b0865de3" type="button" aria-hidden="true" data-testid="expandable-text-button"><span><span><span class="bec82545">…</span><span>more</span></span></span></button></span></p><div class="f3515eab _4b609a84 _3bdd1028 a36d0895 d30fe69e ca3fd208 c6fbc6a9 fda86fa0 _6799957f _0220a842 e1914907 _343dfda4 f7f51821 da961651 _777f6ea0 _3035098d e1496fcf _43a6180d"><a tabindex="0" class="f7f51821 _49812a6b ec50488b bd116eb9 _8a8d57fc _7eb8aec9 e89831ee _997be4da _8a7f68a7 _8301dc9e e3cab0ec ee6d0e13 e7886ddf" href="https://www.linkedin.com/feed/" componentkey="c33ef020-9df6-4cff-9082-ea40ffe99782"><figure class="_88ea701d e40eaae0 e1496fcf _4e20cdcd" componentkey="c33ef020-9df6-4cff-9082-ea40ffe99782"><img class="_975b5252 f50af4d4 fe0126e9 _4e20cdcd _82cb216e dffc9999" fetchpriority="low" alt="View image" src="https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQE30Ebpt_5BZw/feedshare-image-high-res/B56Z6byyfqJoAU-/0/1780730243296?e=1782345600&amp;v=beta&amp;t=6XTSjcGoe6AZ34LztotOHUK5a6JgDwWOY5N7mky9X1A"/><